---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sentinel Nexus | AI Implementation, Security & Governance">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="tagline" id="tagline">Implement. Secure. Govern.</p>
      <h1>AI transformation without the risk.</h1>
      <p class="hero-description">
        We implement AI that works, protect what you build, and ensure it meets governance standards before regulators come knocking. The full AI lifecycle—one trusted partner.
      </p>
      <ContactForm />
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    // Alternating tagline animation
    const taglines = [
      'Implement. Secure. Govern.',
      'Automate. Orchestrate. Operate.'
    ];
    let taglineIndex = 0;
    const taglineEl = document.getElementById('tagline');

    setInterval(() => {
      taglineEl?.classList.add('tagline-fade-out');
      setTimeout(() => {
        taglineIndex = (taglineIndex + 1) % taglines.length;
        if (taglineEl) taglineEl.textContent = taglines[taglineIndex];
        taglineEl?.classList.remove('tagline-fade-out');
      }, 500);
    }, 6000);
  </script>

  <!-- Value Proposition Section -->
  <section class="section" id="why">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Organizations Choose Sentinel Nexus</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        AI is transforming every industry—but most organizations are stuck between fear and hype. They don't know where to start, how to secure what they build, or how to stay compliant as regulations evolve.
      </p>

      <div class="value-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Not Just Consultants</h3>
          <p>We don't deliver reports and walk away. We build, deploy, and manage AI solutions that drive measurable results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Not Just Vendors</h3>
          <p>We don't push tools without context. We understand your business first, then architect solutions that fit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Not Just Security</h3>
          <p>We don't bolt AI onto legacy services. We've rebuilt our practice for the AI era from the ground up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="closing-statement">
        We are the operational partner for the AI era—combining hands-on implementation, security expertise, and governance rigor in a single, integrated offering.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Pillars Section -->
  <section class="section section-dark" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">One Partner. Three Critical Capabilities.</h2>

      <div class="pillars-grid">
        <!-- Pillar 1 -->
        <div class="pillar-card pillar-1">
          <div class="pillar-icon">1</div>
          <h3>AI Implementation & Automation</h3>
          <h4>Build AI That Actually Works</h4>
          <p>From opportunity identification to production deployment, we implement intelligent automation that drives efficiency, reduces costs, and creates competitive advantage.</p>
          <ul class="pillar-services">
            <li>AI readiness assessments and opportunity mapping</li>
            <li>Workflow automation and process redesign</li>
            <li>Agentic Orchestration and Agentic Automation</li>
            <li>Custom AI/ML solution development</li>
            <li>Custom Agentic AI Orchestration Platforms</li>
            <li>System integration (ERP, CRM, ITSM)</li>
            <li>Intelligent document processing</li>
            <li>Conversational AI deployment</li>
            <li>Hyperautomation strategy</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="pillar-outcome">Faster operations. Reduced costs. Competitive edge.</p>
          <a href="/ai-implementation" class="pillar-link">Learn More &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 2 -->
        <div class="pillar-card pillar-2">
          <div class="pillar-icon">2</div>
          <h3>AI Digital Security & MDR</h3>
          <h4>Protect What You Build</h4>
          <p>AI systems create new attack surfaces. We secure your AI infrastructure, protect the data it touches, and provide 24/7 threat detection and response built for modern architectures.</p>
          <ul class="pillar-services">
            <li>AI-enhanced threat detection and response</li>
            <li>Secure AI model development and deployment</li>
            <li>Managed Detection and Response (MDR)</li>
            <li>AI/ML model security and data poisoning prevention</li>
            <li>Cloud security posture management</li>
            <li>Identity and access management</li>
            <li>Vulnerability management and penetration testing</li>
            <li>Incident response and forensics</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="pillar-outcome">Resilience. Threat visibility. Rapid response.</p>
          <a href="/ai-security" class="pillar-link">Learn More &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 3 -->
        <div class="pillar-card pillar-3">
          <div class="pillar-icon">3</div>
          <h3>Responsible AI Governance & Compliance</h3>
          <h4>Govern Before Regulators Require It</h4>
          <p>The EU AI Act is here. NIST AI RMF is the benchmark. We help you build governance frameworks that ensure your AI operates ethically, legally, and with full stakeholder trust.</p>
          <ul class="pillar-services">
            <li>AI policy and framework development</li>
            <li>Algorithmic impact assessments</li>
            <li>Bias detection and fairness auditing</li>
            <li>Data privacy and protection strategies involving AI</li>
            <li>AI Risk and Governance Assessments</li>
            <li>Model documentation and explainability</li>
            <li>Regulatory compliance (EU AI Act, NIST AI RMF, ISO 42001)</li>
            <li>AI risk management programs</li>
            <li>Executive governance training</li>
            <li>Third-party AI vendor risk assessments</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="pillar-outcome">Regulatory readiness. Risk reduction. Stakeholder trust.</p>
          <a href="/ai-governance" class="pillar-link">Learn More &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries Section -->
  <section class="section" id="industries">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for Organizations Ready to Lead with AI</h2>

      <div class="industries-grid">
        <div class="industry-card">
          <h3>Mid-Market Enterprises</h3>
          <span class="industry-label">500–5,000 employees</span>
          <p>You want AI's benefits but lack the internal expertise to execute safely. We become your AI team—implementing, securing, and governing so you can compete with larger players.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="industry-card">
          <h3>Regulated Industries</h3>
          <span class="industry-label">Healthcare, Finance, Insurance, Government</span>
          <p>Your compliance burden is already heavy. Adding AI can't add risk. We ensure every AI initiative meets regulatory requirements from day one.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="industry-card">
          <h3>Technology Companies</h3>
          <span class="industry-label">SaaS, AI-native, Fintechs</span>
          <p>You're moving fast. Security and governance need to catch up—without slowing you down. We build guardrails that enable speed, not restrict it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="industry-card">
          <h3>Private Equity Portfolio Companies</h3>
          <span class="industry-label">Growth-stage businesses</span>
          <p>Your sponsors want AI-driven value creation with disciplined risk management. We deliver both: transformation that drives returns with governance that protects them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Engagement Models -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Flexible Engagement. Measurable Outcomes.</h2>

      <div class="engagement-grid">
        <div class="engagement-card">
          <span class="engagement-duration">2–4 weeks</span>
          <h3>Discovery Sprint</h3>
          <p>Identify your highest-impact AI opportunities. We assess your current state, map automation potential, evaluate security posture, and deliver a prioritized roadmap.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="engagement-card">
          <span class="engagement-duration">2–6 months</span>
          <h3>Implementation Project</h3>
          <p>Design, build, and deploy. We take solutions from concept through production with full security and governance baked in from the start.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="engagement-card">
          <span class="engagement-duration">Ongoing</span>
          <h3>Managed Services</h3>
          <p>Ongoing partnership. From MDR and 24/7 monitoring to continuous automation optimization and fractional AI governance leadership.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="engagement-card">
          <span class="engagement-duration">As needed</span>
          <h3>Assessment & Advisory</h3>
          <p>Point-in-time evaluations. Security assessments, compliance gap analysis, AI risk evaluations, and executive governance training.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Built on Proven Frameworks</h2>

      <div class="frameworks-grid">
        <div class="framework-badge">NIST AI RMF</div>
        <div class="framework-badge">EU AI Act Ready</div>
        <div class="framework-badge">ISO 42001</div>
        <div class="framework-badge">NIST CSF</div>
        <div class="framework-badge">SOC 2</div>
      </div>

      <p class="trust-statement">
        Our methodologies are grounded in industry-leading frameworks. We don't invent new standards—we operationalize the ones that matter.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section section-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Implement AI With Confidence?</h2>
      <p>Let's discuss where AI can drive the most value in your organization—and how to do it securely and responsibly.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" data-umami-event="{Index |Get Started Btn}">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Common Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>We're not sure if we're ready for AI. Can you help us figure that out?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. Our Discovery Sprint is designed exactly for this. In 2–4 weeks, we assess your current state, identify high-impact opportunities, and deliver a prioritized roadmap—whether you're just exploring or ready to move.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How is this different from hiring an AI consulting firm?</h3>
          <p>Consultants deliver recommendations. We deliver results. We don't just assess and advise—we implement, secure, and manage. You get a partner who's accountable for outcomes, not just deliverables.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do we need all three pillars, or can we engage for just one?</h3>
          <p>Our services are modular. Many clients start with one pillar and expand as needs evolve. That said, we believe the pillars work best together—secure implementation and proactive governance prevent costly rework later.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What industries do you specialize in?</h3>
          <p>We work across sectors but have deep experience in regulated industries (healthcare, financial services, insurance, government) where compliance requirements make governance non-negotiable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do you handle AI governance when regulations are still evolving?</h3>
          <p>We design governance programs around established frameworks (NIST AI RMF, ISO 42001, OECD Principles) that align with emerging regulations like the EU AI Act. This approach ensures you're ahead of requirements rather than scrambling to catch up.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What's your approach to AI security—is it different from traditional cybersecurity?</h3>
          <p>AI systems introduce unique risks: model theft, data poisoning, adversarial attacks, and expanded data exposure. Our security practice addresses these AI-specific threats while building on proven cybersecurity fundamentals. It's not either/or—it's both.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section section-final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The AI era is here. Is your organization ready?</h2>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" data-umami-event="{Index | Lets Talk Btn}">Let's Talk</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8rem 0 1rem;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, #1a1a2e 0%, var(--color-bg) 70%);
  }

  .tagline {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }

  .tagline-fade-out {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 650px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Sections */
  .section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .section-dark {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  /* Reduced top padding for section immediately after hero */
  #why {
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .closing-statement {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 3rem auto 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Value Cards */
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Pillars */
  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pillar-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-1 .pillar-icon {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
  }

  .pillar-2 .pillar-icon {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-accent-2);
  }

  .pillar-3 .pillar-icon {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-accent-3);
  }

  .pillar-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-card h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pillar-card > p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-services {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-services li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .pillar-services li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .pillar-outcome {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .pillar-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pillar-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* Industries */
  .industries-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .industry-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .industry-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .industry-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .industry-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Engagement */
  .engagement-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .engagement-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .engagement-duration {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(207, 21, 21, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .engagement-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .engagement-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Frameworks */
  .frameworks-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .framework-badge {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .trust-statement {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .section-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #8b0000 100%);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-cta p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .section-cta .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .section-cta .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f0f0f0;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Final CTA */
  .section-final-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-final-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .pillars-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
